H0.text: Hedonophobia is the irrational fear of what. Pleasure

H1.text: Hedonophobia is the irrational fear of what. Indulgence

H2.text: Hedonophobia is the irrational fear of what. Desire

H3.text: Hedonophobia is the irrational fear of what. Libitum

A4.text: Hedonophobia is an excessive fear or aversion to obtaining pleasure.

A5.text: High anxiety, panic attacks, and extreme fear are symptoms that can result from anticipating pleasure of any kind.
